uage, learns what moves him, learns that she has something he wants beyond her body. And she trades.\n\nYour princess takes a different path \u2014 more direct, more violent, more immediately satisfying. But she'll face the same next problem: now what? A cracked skull heals. A humiliated prince remembers. The political machinery that put her there hasn't changed.\n\nBoth approaches are valid for different characters. Daenerys had no candlestick, no moment where his grip loosened. Your princess did.\n\nThe thread connecting them: neither accepts the role written for them. They just rewrite it differently.\n\nAre you planning to give your princess a longer arc where she has to navigate the fallout through politics and guile, or does she stay the type who solves problems with blunt instruments?", "embedding": [-0.08164121955633163, 0.013463526032865047, 0.09866523742675781, 0.077419713139534, -0.050556961447000504, 0.027570577338337898, 0.025769595056772232, 0.0754719004034996, 0.05422746017575264, 0.034608304500579834, -0.0923418328166008, 0.011819371022284031, -0.026762129738926888, -0.0940929502248764, -0.000571739103179425, 0.021330198273062706, 0.045092422515153885, 0.017011752352118492, -0.11158084124326706, 0.07338046282529831, 0.07009714096784592, -0.09722092002630234, 0.056254349648952484, -0.02510487101972103, -0.07083363831043243, -0.06529532372951508, -0.020238520577549934, 0.0860462635755539, -0.036405038088560104, -0.05935269221663475, 0.03555658087134361, -0.08245988935232162, -0.010570176877081394, 0.0626702755689621, -0.114499032497406, 0.11870431154966354, 0.04127560183405876, 0.016672126948833466, 0.0038576344959437847, 0.038939233869314194, 0.03250112757086754, 0.029433950781822205, -0.04466639831662178, 0.048473358154296875, -0.008412543684244156, -0.03369829058647156, -0.07419002801179886, -0.03916152939200401, -0.056454066187143326, -0.09064327925443649, -0.030405014753341675, 0.07688145339488983, 0.024114469066262245, -0.005899075418710709, -0.0